              i.bi.bi-megaphone
            |系統公告
          .sb-sidenav-menu-heading 選課系統相關
          a.nav-link(href='../additional_selection/')
            .sb-nav-link-icon
              i.bi.bi-file-earmark-plus
            |加選
          a.nav-link(href='../advanced_course/')
            .sb-nav-link-icon
              i.bi.bi-file-earmark-plus-fill
