          a.nav-link(href='../withdraw/')
            .sb-nav-link-icon
              i.bi.bi-file-earmark-minus
            |退選
          a.nav-link(href='../curriculum/')
            .sb-nav-link-icon
              i.bi.bi-calendar2-check-fill
            |檢視以選修科目
          a.nav-link(href='../change_password/')
            .sb-nav-link-icon
              i.bi.bi-lock
            |更改密碼
